# The Inferno Curse - Project Rules
- Player character: 13th-century Catholic priest, 32-bit pixel art sprite (res://assets/images/priest_sprite.png)
- Game: 3D HD / HD-2D RPG foundation using orthographic 3D scenes with pixel-art billboard characters.
- Color palette: deep golds, shadow blues, warm burnt oranges, dark moody aesthetic
- Main scene: res://scenes/main.tscn -- medieval tavern interior
- Active scene root uses Node3D, Camera3D, CharacterBody3D, StaticBody3D, and OmniLight3D.
- Player movement is on the XZ plane via CharacterBody3D move_and_slide.
- Keep the current phase focused on 3D HD engine setup, camera, lighting, collision, and visual readability.
